text: The 2016–17 Moldovan "B" Division () was the 26th season of Moldovan football's third-tier league. A total of 29 teams competed in this division. The season began on 27 August 2016 and ended on 2 June 2017. The league consisted of two regional groups, Nord (North) and Sud (South). ==League table== === North === === Results === === South === === Results === ==References== ==External links== * Divizia B - Results, fixtures, tables and news - Soccerway Category:Moldovan "B" Division seasons 3 Moldova 3
